---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="FAQ - DayDreamHub" description="Frequently asked questions about day-use hotel booking on DayDreamHub.">

<section class="bg-teal-50 py-16 sm:py-20"> <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center"> <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
Frequently Asked Questions
</h1> <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
Find answers to common questions about day-use hotel booking on DayDreamHub.
</p> </div> </section>  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16"> <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6"> <div class="space-y-10"> <div> <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"> <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold flex-shrink-0"> 1 </span> Basic Information About Day Use Hotels </h2> <div class="space-y-3"> <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">What is a Day Use Hotel?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> A Day Use Hotel is a service where hotel rooms can be used during specific daytime hours, different from regular overnight stays. Usage includes short breaks, work, or waiting time. Stays typically last a few hours to half a day without overnight accommodation. </div> </details> </div> </div><div> <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"> <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold flex-shrink-0"> 2 </span> Reservation Method </h2> <div class="space-y-3"> <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">How do I make a reservation?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> Search for a hotel, select a plan, choose dates and guest count, then proceed to booking. </div> </details><details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">What time slots are available?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> Time slots vary by hotel and plan. Each listing shows available check-in and check-out times. </div> </details><details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">Can I book for my family?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> Yes, check the max guests for each plan. For additional guests, contact the hotel directly. </div> </details><details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">Can I reserve multiple rooms?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> Yes, you can make separate bookings for multiple rooms. </div> </details> </div> </div><div> <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"> <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold flex-shrink-0"> 3 </span> Payment Questions </h2> <div class="space-y-3"> <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">Do I need a credit card?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> PayPal is our primary payment method. Some hotels accept onsite payment. </div> </details><details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">When am I charged?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> Prepayment is required for plans marked as such. Onsite payment plans are paid at check-in. </div> </details><details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">What if my prepayment reservation is denied?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> A full refund will be issued to your PayPal account. </div> </details><details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">Can I pay at check-in?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> For plans marked &quot;onsite payment&quot;, yes. Prepayment plans require PayPal. </div> </details> </div> </div><div> <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"> <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold flex-shrink-0"> 4 </span> Reservation Changes &amp; Cancellation </h2> <div class="space-y-3"> <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">How do I confirm my reservation?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> A confirmation email is sent after booking. This serves as your booking documentation. </div> </details><details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">Can I cancel my reservation?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> Cancellation policies vary by hotel. Check the specific hotel&#39;s policy. </div> </details><details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">Can I change dates?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> Contact the hotel directly for date changes. </div> </details><details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">What if I arrive late?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> Contact the hotel. Late arrivals may affect your available time. </div> </details><details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">Can I get early check-in or late checkout?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> Subject to availability. Contact the hotel directly. </div> </details> </div> </div><div> <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"> <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold flex-shrink-0"> 5 </span> Account and Privacy </h2> <div class="space-y-3"> <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">Why do I need an account?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> Accounts are created automatically during booking to manage your reservations. </div> </details><details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">How is my data protected?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> We follow strict privacy policies. See our Privacy Policy page. </div> </details><details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">Can I delete my account?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> Yes, but deletion will cancel any active reservations. </div> </details><details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"> <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-5 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base"> <span class="pr-4">How do I unsubscribe from emails?</span> <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="px-5 pb-4 pt-1 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50"> Use the unsubscribe link in any newsletter email. </div> </details> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section>  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-gray-50"> <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center"> <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
Still have questions?
</h2> <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">
Contact our support team and we'll be happy to help.
</p> <a href="mailto:customer@daydreamhub.com" class="text-teal-700 hover:underline font-medium">
customer@daydreamhub.com
</a> </div> </section>


</Layout>
